msgid "Scenario IV: Return to The Boundary Beyond"
msgstr "冒险IV：重返界限彼端"

msgid "Combine the new [[Present-Day]] locations with the original versions from <i>The Boundary Beyond</i>. Remove 1 of the 2 copies of each location from the game at random. Then put Metropolitan Cathedral, Zócalo, Temple Ruins, Xochimilco, Chapultepec Park, and Coyoacán into play. Each investigator begins play in either Zócalo or Coyoacán (their choice)."
msgstr "将新版的[[现代]]地点加入原版<i>界限彼端</i>遭遇组的地点中。将每个地点的2张卡牌中的随机1张从游戏中移除。然后将大都会教堂、索卡洛广场、神庙遗迹、霍奇米尔科、查普尔特佩克公园、科约阿坎区放置入场。每位调查员任意选择索卡洛广场或科约阿坎区开始游戏。"

msgid "Create the exploration deck. This is done by taking the 12 single-sided [[Ancient]] locations and shuffling them together. Do not include any of the other encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions."
msgstr "构建探索牌堆。使用12张单面的[[古代]]地点。不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。"
